(737, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Mais populares</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/''>UpdraftPlus - WordPress Backup and Restoration</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=3b18e6cb2a&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''UpdraftPlus - WordPress Backup and Restoration''>Instalar</a>)</span>\n<p>Easy and complete backups + restoration. Manual or automated backups (backup to S3, Dropbox, Google Drive, Rackspace, FTP, SFTP, email + others).</p>\n<h4>Plugins mais recentes</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/fetch-tweets-hashtag-cloud/''>Fetch Tweets - Hashtag Cloud</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=fetch-tweets-hashtag-cloud&amp;_wpnonce=464124f3e5&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''Fetch Tweets - Hashtag Cloud''>Instalar</a>)</span>\n<p>Extracts and displays only hastags from the result of Fetch Tweets.</p>\n', 'no'),
